mindmap
  root((Architecture Review Scorecard))
    Functional Fit
      User stories satisfied
      Edge cases handled
      Acceptance criteria measurable
    Architectural Fit
      Aligns to platform patterns
      Reuses existing services
      Conforms to ADR catalogue
    NFR Coverage
      Targets specified per attribute
      Trade-offs articulated
      Validation pathway exists
    Operability
      Runbooks for top failures
      Telemetry instrumented
      Deployment rollback rehearsed
    Security and Compliance
      Threat model current
      Controls mapped to ISMS
      Data classifications applied
    Cost and Sustainability
      Cost estimate documented
      Carbon footprint considered
      Capacity headroom planned
